{"data":[{"id":563104367,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"cd1372650d71e6ccbed79063dceef58b","url_token":"wu-yao-wang-zhi-lei","name":"巫妖王之泪","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-2c59ec55f500b8c3c560ba2ca124bc57_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-2c59ec55f500b8c3c560ba2ca124bc57_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/cd1372650d71e6ccbed79063dceef58b","user_type":"people","headline":"真理追求者，世界创造者，幻想者","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":108,"is_followed":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/563104367","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546181844,"updated_time":1546182293,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":17,"comment_count":1,"is_sticky":false,"admin_closed_comment":false,"comment_permission":"all","can_comment":{"reason":"","status":true},"reshipment_settings":"allowed","content":"\u003cp\u003e肯定是失败，不存在成功的可能性，最微小的可能性都没有，就是零。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e这没什么好说的。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我想说的是，那些在评论区对他进行鼓励的人，那些对这个孩子吹鼓所谓的“梦想”的人，那些对这个孩子说什么相信自己，“他只是个孩子要鼓励”的人。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e非蠢既坏!\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e当然，大多数只是蠢。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e几万人的冷嘲热讽才是正常的。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e这总比鼓励他，吹鼓所谓的梦想好。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e这孩子最后要是成为一个民科，或者在你们所谓的鼓励之下专注哥猜忽视高考。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e你们很可能就把这个孩子毁了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e你们根本不知道证明哥猜的难度，没有对这种困扰人类智力最顶尖那群人几百年的难题有着最基本的敬畏。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e一个高中生宣称用基本数学证明哥猜。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e这根本就是一种侮辱。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e侮辱1742年至今为止的数学界，侮辱欧拉高数希尔伯特等等这些人类古往今来的智力最高峰。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e你们这种鼓励相当于对一个跑万米马拉松的新生儿喊加油。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e你们是在害了他。\u003c/p\u003e","editable_content":"